Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,While the night is brief, \Nit comes around again soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we've been able to endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how badly our days may go, \Nas long as we have the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...as long as we have Vanguard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...we can fight through it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have our friends \Nfrom Team Blackout....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This place was our hangout spot.  \NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't know much about each other's \Nlife situations, and we wouldn't pry.\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't know much about each other's \Nlife situations, and we wouldn't pry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all for the best. \NWhat connected us was Vanguard. A card game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In this place, everything \Nwas decided using Vanguard. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And with the cards between us, \Nwe'd have conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Until that day, the day this place got wrecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I read book after book.  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The nights were long without everyone around, \Nand reading was the only thing I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here where we live, \Nthe city of Kanazawa in the land of Kaga,  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we have a capture-the-flag game called Hatagenpei:\Na battle between the Genji and the Heishi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In this area, the famous warrior Saito Sanemori\Nstaked his life on a hopeless battle. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm neither Genji nor Heishi, \Nmuch less a military commander.  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The pity of it \NTrapped underneath a HELMET \NA grasshopper chirps\NI'm neither Genji nor Heishi, \Nmuch less a military commander.  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I failed to protect the Blackout banner, \Nlosing the battle wouldn't cost me my life. \NThe pity of it \NTrapped underneath a HELMET \NA grasshopper chirps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I failed to protect the Blackout banner, \Nlosing the battle wouldn't cost me my life. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet... 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...why does it hurt like I'm dying? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how I try to empty my mind, \Nthe painful feelings keep getting in. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Tohya not understand that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Tohya's the one \Nwho destroyed the merry-go-round.  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And now he's the one fixing it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The nights are long without everyone around. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And worse, they come around again soon enough.  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The nights are long \Nwhen you're by yourself. Too long...  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days has Tohya been here, all alone? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Exspecta vs Bastion\NReboot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wonder Hill \N Let's Have Lots of Fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The pity of it \NTrapped underneath a HELMET \NA grasshopper chirps
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A new... banner?\NThe pity of it \NTrapped underneath a HELMET \NA grasshopper chirps
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, say--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to help me.\NUh, say--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I caused all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm atoning for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can manage this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird running into anyone here \Nat this time of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's the banner that Takami made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Blackout's banner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that Danji still has it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot happened back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that only the light bulbs were broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to replace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not angry, Tomari?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, Blackout has lots of naughty kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And Danji was one too, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto and Ishida \Nhave also settled down, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you talked with Tohya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you haven't heard the thing \Nabout him and his university?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he quit in order to play cards seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me, "I went that far, to come here."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu, are you angry with Tohya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But weren't you offering to help fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...because Tohya was also worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And he seemed to be suffering. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the type who'd forgive a girl \Nwho cheats on you if she cries, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were my words of sisterly advice for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Work to Do Every Day \N #1: Feed Melonbread \N #2: Take out trash \N #3 Clean bath
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Feed Melonbread.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Trash and Recycling Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Number two.\NTrash and Recycling Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Number three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Odd Jobs by Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Odd Jobs by Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji will be away from home for a good while,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so he's letting me stay here in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're taking over his gig work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I do have to pay for \Nthe repairs, and the electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I could help--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to help.\NI could help--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I caused a lot of trouble for Danji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to take care of all this myself, \Nfor it to count as atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari was telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you're trying to take care \Nof everything all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's impossible, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Odd Jobs by Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Odd Jobs by Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen Danji do this job before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I'm done, I'll help you out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, as soon as I'm done, \NI'll be right over to help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even able to climb a tree earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not gonna lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you carry even one of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be a piece of cake for me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to work out... this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Awww, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the work \NDanji does is horribly tough?\NAwww, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Awww, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Will those two be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Substituting for Danji is... \Na bit too much... for ordinary people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you back again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can't leave you to do it all yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who'd impede any progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you failed at everything yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya, you're somewhat... ordinary, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You struck me as someone more perfect, and scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a bit relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm embarrassed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing nothing but failing, \Nunable to get anything right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we do our best together a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak of the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the sudden request!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you memorized your dance moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on in five minutes, \Nso we'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do my best at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But not doing it isn't an option, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiddie Showtime
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, I can't wait!\NKiddie Showtime
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it gonna be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed yet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what were you doing out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant!\NWe're terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be calling on you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is! A Big Kani-Kani Parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kani"? Crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what Danji orders \Non his way home from work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji says, "It'd be no exaggeration \Nto call this my reason for working!" 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to dance, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Only thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything without you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, we really ought \Nto reinforce the scaffolding...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only here because Yu-yu asked me to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought fixing this place \Nwas too much for the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto's really good at hammering!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:12:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He taught me how to do it \Nwhen we built the barricades.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ishida's stronger than he looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff that we can't carry, he can, easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, it's mostly in working order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling it's even \Nmore splendid than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but... what about the electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Danji's not here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I paid the electric bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I used the money I earned working with Yu-yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be back on tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, say... we've got some time \Nbefore tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place I'd like to go visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Card Shop Stray Cat \NHigh Prices for Used    Battle Space Available!! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been here in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a pack I want to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya, please look around in here while you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at these!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything in the new cards grabbing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, when playing Keter, \NI'd have to go with Lagrele, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lagrele is high-cost and difficult to use, \Nand its strength depends a lot on luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's what's great about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun because it depends on luck, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight with everything \Nriding on luck can be a great time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds right up your alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What d'you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I robbed you all of your place to play Vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am very sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's all fixed now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're getting our electricity back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, the lights are back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackout is finally reactivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get it entirely back \Nto how it was before, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing that's been broken \Nwill go back to the way it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what "scrap and rebuild" is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rebuild it to be even stronger than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By which I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go up there and give us a real fight, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Got your new card?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All set?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! It's a fight to launch Blackout \Ninto a brand new restart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They each have one win \Nand one loss against the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who wins, \Nthis'll be Taking-the-Lead Fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari's more exuberant than usual tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I kinda get why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm also happy \Nto be able to fight like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We'll dispense with the details!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,While we fight, I'm gonna give you full leeway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...overDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also fine for me to \Nbeat you to a pulp, right, Tohya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're able to say that, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? \NAre you guys youth-ing it up?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go leaving me behind, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari's not commentating at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's totally heckling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Bastion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too soon for you to fight the way Danji does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You were wrong to assume \Nyou'd clinch this perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you'll mess up soon enough, Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?! You were talking about something \Nbesides cards there, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, maybe not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, you really have gotten saucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! A series of attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With the effect, Alden's power rises, \Ninflicting a fierce sword blow on Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,OverDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, another overDress! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's where Yu-yu's new card shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Vairina's final evolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, who knows \Nhow the fight will proceed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! That's the way!\NNow you're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him! Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll have Nirvana attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya's not guarding at this point?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a critical, it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what strategy is he following this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'm not...\NJust what strategy is he following this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll end it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Front trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Front trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Critical denied!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Was the "no guard" \Nbecause he foresaw this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, If I'd done an incomplete guard, \NI wouldn't have been able to block on this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an accident, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be full someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That entire audience space!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Exspecta attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,With its skill, it has two criticals, \Nand its power is 73,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiyu attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard with two Gurgants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?! Wha the huh?! He held it off completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! So he saw that development coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So he staked it on a critical not appearing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fights can be like this, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona Ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I call Lagrele!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This time Tohya calls in a new card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Knight's Squad's newest recruit \Nhas joined the fray!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Alden attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With the skill, his total shield is 40,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a double trigger will get through now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, he drew a double trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now even Tohya's all go-go-go, shove-shove!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to clinch a win \Nwith his last attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lagrele attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I activate its skill to gain a drive check!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, I must discard my entire hand \Nafter this battle ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staking it all on this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting with your back to the wall, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a perfect guard, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu actually had one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now even if Tohya draws a trigger, \Nhis attack won't go through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet! Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Check...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A grade 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With Bastion's skill, I restand Alden!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He had that trick available?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya can attack once more with Alden!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Heavenly Sword! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, just try stopping it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going at full strength! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rise to your challenge! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Exspecta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't know if I was able \Nto forgive you seriously, Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, I'm somehow having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this violent throbbing in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this radiance in my chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...what Danji was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?! \NAm I breaking into a grin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's clinch this, Exspecta! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is everything I am right now! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible! No guard, at 4 damage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:23:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For real, just how far ahead \Nhad you read the game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.34,0:23:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got great luck, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, that fight was red-hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If only your luck was as great as his, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was uncalled for!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.86,0:25:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.95,0:25:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.66,0:25:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.57,0:25:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tohya.\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.43,0:25:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll introduce \NHeavenly Shock of Distinction, Lagrele.\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.76,0:25:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when this card attacks a Vanguard, you can \Nrest your units to give it drive checks. 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.47,0:26:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's a penalty based on how many \Nother rear-guards you rest when it attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.39,0:26:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, here's the trick to mastering this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.15,0:26:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you rest four units, you don't discard any of \Nyour hand, but you get fewer attacks that round.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.56,0:26:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you rest two units, you don't lose attacks, \Nbut your total number in hand is reduced by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.47,0:26:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't rest even one unit, \Nyou discard five cards from your hand, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.60,0:26:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.82,0:26:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.56,0:26:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maiden Mannerism\NReconciliation 
